DestroyModuleConfig ButtonsPager:*
*ButtonsPager: Geometry $[infostore.PanelWidth]x$[infostore.PanelPagerHeight]-$[infostore.PanelGap]+$[infostore.PanelOffsetTop]
*ButtonsPager: Colorset 10
*ButtonsPager: Rows 90
*ButtonsPager: Columns 125
*ButtonsPager: Frame $[infostore.PanelFrame]
*ButtonsPager: Font $[infostore.PanelFont]
*ButtonsPager: (5x90, Action(Mouse 1) Next (CirculateHit, ButtonsPager) PipeRead 'echo LockingSlide $$(test $$(($[w.x]+$[w.width])) -le $[vp.width] && echo w$$(($[w.width]-$width+$[infostore.PanelGap]-$[infostore.PanelHideWidth]))p || echo w-$$(($[w.width]-$width+$[infostore.PanelGap]-$[infostore.PanelHideWidth]))p) keep')
*ButtonsPager: (120x5, Frame 0)
*ButtonsPager: (5x80, Frame 0)
*ButtonsPager: (110x80, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', frame $[infostore.PanelFrame])
*ButtonsPager: (5x80, Frame 0)
*ButtonsPager: (120x5, Frame 0)
AddPanelOffsetTop $[infostore.PanelPagerHeight]

# FvwmPager
#
# This module displays the location of the windows on the various Pages
# and Desks. This is setup to show only the Pages on the current Desk.
DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPager:*
*FvwmPager: Colorset * 10
*FvwmPager: HilightColorset * 13
*FvwmPager: BalloonColorset * 10
*FvwmPager: WindowColorsets 10 11
*FvwmPager: Font None
*FvwmPager: Balloons All
*FvwmPager: BalloonFont $[infostore.PanelFont]
*FvwmPager: BallonYOffset +2
*FvwmPager: Window3dBorders
*FvwmPager: MiniIcons
*FvwmPager: SolidSeparators

Module FvwmButtons ButtonsPager
